Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.81,0:02:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}關於關谷純
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你舅舅的葬禮怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.43,0:02:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}已經順利結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.62,0:02:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.43,0:02:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.13,0:02:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.13,0:02:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}折木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.80,0:02:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果方便的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:02:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要不要來給舅舅上炷香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:02:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.25,0:02:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.34,0:03:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}最近打算去祭拜一下舅舅的墳墓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.61,0:03:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個 可以的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.64,0:03:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能一起去…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.11,0:03:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.77,0:03:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.45,0:03:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.86,0:03:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼 具體日期再另行通知了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.77,0:03:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.03,0:03:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}舅舅的那件事也是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}折木同學總能完美地解開謎題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的覺得你很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.01,0:03:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說我運氣好倒沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.67,0:03:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要說我是了不起的傢伙 還是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.05,0:03:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你真是謙虛呢 折木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.69,0:03:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 還真是啊 完全沒領會我的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.65,0:03:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}千反田 古人說得好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.74,0:03:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.99,0:03:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}「道理和紗布不論哪裡都能貼」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}折木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.99,0:04:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個諺語是「道理和藥布」喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.12,0:04:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.95,0:04:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}反正道理是總能搬得出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.33,0:04:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.76,0:04:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}折木同學能順利解決這一連串的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.22,0:04:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}並不是因為有才能 就當作是運氣好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.43,0:04:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 根據線索進行推理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.02,0:04:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}並能引導出推測 這不能認為是一種才能嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.47,0:04:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你說我是推理的達人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.81,0:04:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼會得出推測呢 連我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.56,0:04:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是因為折木同學沒有好好審視過自我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.18,0:04:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖說如此 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.63,0:04:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼 千反田
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.04,0:04:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你隨便給出一個情況吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.41,0:04:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我來證明給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}無論什麼事我都能搬出一番通道理！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}聽起來很有意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.48,0:05:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這正好個機會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.07,0:05:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我就讓你明白我可不是那麼可靠的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼 要出什麼題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.23,0:05:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}10月31日 在車站前的巧文堂買過東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.18,0:05:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}並與某事有關之人
